    <h1>eZ Platform 15.12.1 Release Notes</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>The first sub-release of <a href=3D"/display/DEVELOPER/eZ+Platfo=
rm+15.12+Release+notes">eZ Platform 15.12</a> is now available for update.<=
/p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-not=
e">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-info=
rmation-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p>For the release notes of the corresponding eZ Studio sub-release, see <a=
 href=3D"/display/DEVELOPER/eZ+Studio+15.12.1+Release+notes">eZ Studio 15.1=
2.1 Release Notes</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"eZPlatform15.12.1ReleaseNotes-Changessince15.12">Changes since 15=
.12</h2>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-war=
ning">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-error confluence-inform=
ation-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p>As already deprecated on <a href=3D"https://doc.ez.no/pages/viewpage.act=
ion?pageId=3D31429536" rel=3D"nofollow">requirements</a> page, this release=
 <strong>does not support PHP 5.4</strong> any longer.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p>For list of issues fixed in 15.12.1 see<span class=3D"static-jira-issues=
_count"> <a class=3D"issue-link" href=3D"https://jira.ez.no/secure/IssueNav=
igator.jspa?reset=3Dtrue&amp;jqlQuery=3DfixVersion+in+%28%222015.12.1%22%29=
+AND+project+%3D+EZP+AND+issuetype+in+%28Story%2C+Improvement%2C+Bug%29+ord=
er+by+issuetype+++++&amp;src=3Dconfmacro"> 13 issues </a> </span> , below i=
s a list of notable bugs/features/enhancements done in the release.&nbsp;</=
p>
<h3 id=3D"eZPlatform15.12.1ReleaseNotes-Distribution">Distribution</h3>
<ul>
<li>Improved Install doc and Apache/Nginx doc, added script to generate vho=
st for automation needs.</li>
<li>PHP Internal web server "works", further fixes in 16.02 to make it test=
ed and supported for dev use.</li>
<li>Installers don't write to config anymore, only folders mentioned in dir=
ectory permissions are written to.</li>
<li>Info on where to find <a href=3D"https://github.com/ezsystems/ezplatfor=
m-demo" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">demo install</a> of eZ Pla=
tform added.</li>
<li><span style=3D"line-height: 1.42857;">Several improvements done on </sp=
an><a href=3D"http://doc.ez.no" style=3D"line-height: 1.42857;" class=3D"ex=
ternal-link" rel=3D"nofollow">doc.ez.no</a><span style=3D"line-height: 1.42=
857;"> and specifically </span><a href=3D"http://doc.ez.no/display/TECHDOC"=
 style=3D"line-height: 1.42857;" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">d=
oc.ez.no/display/TECHDOC</a>.</li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"eZPlatform15.12.1ReleaseNotes-Kernel">Kernel</h3>
<ul>
<li>[API] Fix publishing to only update modified time, leaving published ti=
me to be time of first publish like in legacy</li>
<li>[Twig] New <strong>ez_field</strong>&nbsp;function, unlike <strong>ez_f=
ield_value</strong> &nbsp;returns whole Field - find more information <a hr=
ef=3D"/display/DEVELOPER/Content+Rendering">here.</a></li>
<li> <span class=3D"jira-issue resolved"> <a href=3D"https://jira.ez.no/bro=
wse/EZP-24467?src=3Dconfmacro" class=3D"jira-issue-key"><img class=3D"icon"=
 src=3D"https://jira.ez.no/images/icons/issuetypes/bug.png">EZP-24467</a> -=
 <span class=3D"summary">[API] When moving an object to an hidden container=
, the moved object doesn't have the hidden by superior status</span>=20
<!-- The new status lozengens support for JIRA 6.2 or later. Otherwise we u=
se the icon.--> <span class=3D"aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-subtle aui-lozenge-s=
uccess jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf">Closed</span> </span> </li>
<li> <span class=3D"jira-issue resolved"> <a href=3D"https://jira.ez.no/bro=
