<li>API doc js-rest-client: <a href=3D"http://ezsystems.github.io/javascrip=
t-rest-client/" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">http://ezsystems.g=
ithub.io/javascript-rest-client/</a></li>
<li>API doc Platform UI: <a href=3D"http://ezsystems.github.io/platformui-j=
avascript-api/" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">http://ezsystems.g=
ithub.io/platformui-javascript-api/</a></li>
<li>Tutorials for extending UI: <a href=3D"https://doc.ez.no/display/TECHDO=
C/Extending+Tutorials" rel=3D"nofollow">https://doc.ez.no/display/TECHDOC/E=
xtending+Tutorials</a></li>
</ul>
